            "id": 6273824,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 奇異(GE-US)大漲5.01%，報302.87美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>奇異(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GE-US</a>)截至台北時間12日23:22股價上漲14.45美元，報302.87美元，漲幅5.01%，成交量2,273,995（股），盤中最高價302.87美元、最低價290.70美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.03%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.62%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.88%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-2.87%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>奇異(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GE-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-2.83%</li> <li>近 1 月：-8.73%</li> <li>近 3 月：+0.68%</li> <li>近 6 月：+15.51%</li> <li>今年以來：+68.22%</li></ul></section></main>",
